# Development Workflow

## Scripts

The project includes various npm scripts for development and building:

- `npm run dev` - Start development server with Vite
- `npm run build` - Build production version
- `npm run build:dev` - Build development version
- `npm run lint` - Run ESLint to check code quality
- `npm run preview` - Preview production build locally
- `npm run generate-sitemap` - Generate sitemap for SEO

## Important Files

- [package.json](mdc:package.json) - Project scripts and dependencies
- [vite.config.ts](mdc:vite.config.ts) - Vite configuration
- [eslint.config.js](mdc:eslint.config.js) - ESLint configuration

## Development Commands

```bash
# Install dependencies
npm install

# Start development server
npm run dev

# Build for production
npm run build

# Preview production build
npm run preview
```
